ry in Ukraine, church leadership, 25+ years field experience, family of six | Field: Ukraine | Comms: March 18, 2026", "fit_score": 9, "fit_reason": "Multiple 2026 posts (March 18, March 11, Aug 31 2025), active personal blog with giving page, overseas personal support", "source_query": "hunter:blog-networks", "meta": {"h": "blog-networks", "src": "https://ofreport.com/", "import_source": "batch3_2.sql"}}]'::jsonb)
